ehambelanayo: Imigca emibini kwisithuba esine-dimensional ezimbini engadibaniyo
inqwelomoya: Umphezulu othe tyaba one-dimensional ezimbini ekunokuthi kulale kuwo izinto ezine-dimensional
inqaku: Indawo ethile emgceni, kwinqwelomoya, okanye esithubeni
icala: Amacandelo omgca kwimizobo yejometri edibanisa ingaphandle yento
umqolo: Indawo apho amacala amabini omfanekiso omacala mabini adibana khona.
isangqa: Imilo emacala mabini apho onke amanqaku kumgca ogobileyo alinganayo ukusuka kwindawo esembindini.
uxande: I-two-dimensional, ivaliwe, isibalo esinamacala amane aneengile ezine ezichanekileyo
isikwere: Uhlobo olukhethekileyo loxande olunamacala alinganayo kunye namacala achaseneyo
ityhubhu: Umfanekiso one-dimensional ezintathu ezinezikwere ezifanayo ezilinganayo njengobuso
